com.teamscale.commons.commit

Class CommitDescriptorTestUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teamscale.commons.commit.CommitDescriptorTestUtils

  • public class CommitDescriptorTestUtils
extends java.lang.Object
    Class providing static imports of methods to create commit descriptors with shorthand methods. Should be used to increase readability of tests.
